---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Transforma tu presencia digital" id="intro">
  <!-- <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="size-32" /> -->
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Impulsa tu negocio con soluciones web <span class="text-primary">integrales</span> que combinan <span class="text-primary">diseño</span> y <span class="text-primary">desarrollo</span> de alto rendimiento. <span class="text-primary">Optimización web</span> y <span class="text-primary">e-commerce personalizado</span> al alcance de tu mano.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="#features"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon name="mdi:tools" class="size-8" />
      <span>Descubre nuestros servicios</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=543515439227&text&type=phone_number&app_absent=0"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon name="mdi:chat" class="size-8" />
      <span>Contacta con nosotros</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>

